 accidental.', 2380, 0), (82386, 'We''re all leaving now", Blue Eyes whispered to her. "Together. Out the front door. Scream, and we''ll kill you here and now."Or later", Willow suggested nervously. "Later would be a big improvement on that idea. We could meet back here in, say, an hour, and you can exhibit your homicidal tendencies then, okay? That would be way better for us.', 17151, 0), (82387, 'Sometime later the islanders on a little rimward atoll were amazed to find, washed into their little local lagoon, the wave-rocked corpse of a hideous sea monster, all beaks, eyes and tentacles. They were further astonished at its size, since it was rather larger than their village. But their surprise was tiny compared to the huge, stricken expression on the face of the dead monster, which appeared to be have been trampled to death. ', 195, 0), (82388, 'It was almost noon when the plane touched down at the Triad airport on the outskirts of Greensboro. There was a hire car waiting for me; I waved my notepad at the dashboard to transmit my profile, then waited as the seating and controls rearranged themselves slightly, piezoelectric actuators humming. As I started to reverse out of the parking bay, the stereo began a soothing improvisation, flashing up a deadpan title: Music for Leaving Airports 11 June 2008.', 13600, 0), (82389, 'Denis could think of no logical reason why he should not attempt to mate with Beth Cooper.There were no laws explicitly against it.They were of the same species, and had complementary sex organs, most likely, based on extensive mental modeling Denis had done.', 17071, 0), (82390, 'God in his infinite wisdomDid not make me very wise-So when my actions are stupidThey hardly take God by surprise.', 1009, 0), (82391, '-I love you, Lenny.-From the diaphragm.-What are you talking about?-You have to say it from the diaphragm. That''s a muscle in here. Real deep, not from the throat. I tried to be an actor once and that''s the first thing they told me. That''s when I quit. I just didn''t have that much in my diaphragm.', 16881, 0), (82392, 'The encapsulated bird your conspirators sent you to fetch. The sterilized male chicken with the Creator DNA sequences. The plot capon. Where is it?', 3736, 0), (82393, 'He''s got a chloroform-soaked rag in one hand, and before Judy realizes what''s happening, the dude is all over her like fat on cheese.', 591, 0), (82394, '...and thus he found his single source of joy in the society of other people: frightening the girls with his penis.', 612, 0), (82395, 'Whew,'' he said, ''I''m glad that''s over, Thomas. I''ve been feeling awfully bad about it.'' It was only too evident that he no longer did.', 429, 0), (82396, 'His jaw was set, telling me I should back off. Unfortunately, being a gobby cow meant I couldn’t.', 6793, 0), (82397, '...we''ve already had one horrible thing happen today, which means that if you think about it the odds of anything else horrible happening again in the next few hours should now be quite low.', 17152, 0), (82398, 'He must have been delightful," she said, "when he was alive!', 17153, 0), (82399, 'He eased back and murmured, “You taste so damn sweet. Like maple syrup.”“And you taste like stolen bacon.', 17154, 0), (82400, 'Tell me you spotted a condom tree over to the right by the stream of lube.', 17155, 0);
